PC Number: 2020-0035

Date: 2020-01-30

Whereas the East Wellington Chamber of Commerce, in Ontario, the certificate of formation of which was recorded pursuant to the Boards of Trade Act on May 12, 2010, has ceased to exercise its franchises;

 

Therefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Industry, pursuant to section 43 of the Boards of Trade Act, dissolves the East Wellington Chamber of Commerce.


 

Attendu que la East Wellington Chamber of Commerce (Ontario), dont le certificat de formation a été enregistré en vertu de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce le 12 mai 2010, a cessé d’exercer ses pouvoirs,

 

À ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de l’Industrie et en vertu de l’article 43 de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil dissout la East Wellington Chamber of Commerce.
